Adding Change Rec Probability Sub-KPI 26

Change Rec Probability



1. Click on an empty space on the canvas, and from the visualizations pane select Card.
2.Drag or select ‘ChangeRecProbability’ into the Fields section.
3. Fill in the figures provided below for the necessary fields.
